    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior has significant rust on the rocker panels and wheel arches, and the paint is heavily oxidized. Mechanically, the engine requires a serious overhaul as it currently struggles to idle, and there are several fluid leaks that need immediate attention. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It is recommended to have the vehicle towed.",
